    "Additionally, various numerical techniques that complement Hartree-Fock, such as DMRG [68], quantum Monte Carlo [87,88], and exact diagonalization [99,100], obtain ground states that are broadly similar to generalized ferromagnets, thereby validating the strong coupling treatment of the interacting BM model.",
    "Complications to the Strong-Coupling FrameworkThe strong-coupling limit of the BM model provides a range of insights into its phase diagram, which is corroborated by numerical studies of the interacting BM model.",
